data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS! ASK ABOUT CREDITS TO BUY DOWN THE RATE OR CLOSING COSTS.  Come see this modern tri level townhouse in the desirable community of Playa Del Sol. Upgrades include luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the entire home, stainless steel appliances, full sized laundry room and a two car garage equipped with 240v plug for EV charging. Upon entry is a private room with your own full bath enclosed with barn style doors that can be used as an office or extra bedroom. The second floor invites you to your spacious main living area and access to your private balcony. Enjoy your open concept kitchen with a dining island, quartz countertops, plenty of cabinet space and a pantry closet. The top floor is where you can find the huge primary bedroom featuring a walk in closet and en suite bathroom with dual vanities and glass shower. The community offers resort style amenities pool/gym/barbecue/clubhouse and it is conveniently located near freeways so you can easily access everything San Diego.
